data.text:
At Westminster Woods on Julington Creek, an active lifestyle meets a beautiful, wooded campus with convenient access to cosmopolitan Jacksonville and St. Johns County. Choose from a variety of spacious residences featuring garden and water views, with garden apartments, mid-rise waterfront apartments, and single-family homes with floor plans to meet your imagination. Just outside your door, exciting wellness and lifelong learning opportunities abound, from American literature to yoga, all part of our exclusive My W Life program. Don’t give home maintenance or chores another thought, with fantastic hospitality services and amenities to enhance your lifestyle. Whether you prefer a boat ride on the half-mile-wide Julington Creek, hitting the books, or going for a dip in the pool, there’s something at Westminster Woods on Julington Creek to make you happy.

Learn how you can make The Natural Choice today! Click here to contact us or call (904) 664-2870 to learn more.
